metadata.abstract: The document titled 'General (englisch)' provides information on two key resources for VATSIM Germany members: Teamspeak 3 and the Forum VATSIM Germany. Teamspeak 3 is a voice communication software widely used by VATSIM members for real-time communication during flight simulations. The document likely includes instructions on how to install, configure, and use Teamspeak 3 effectively. The Forum VATSIM Germany section provides details on the online community platform where members can discuss various topics related to virtual aviation, share experiences, and seek advice. This forum is an essential tool for networking and staying updated with the latest developments within the VATSIM Germany community.
